title: Cuba’s Communist Government Has Lasted 67 Years. Will It Fall Under Trump?
summary_full: The Trump administration, which has tightened the U.S. chokehold on Cuba by cutting off foreign oil, is betting that this is the Cuban communist revolution’s last year.
